(504, 'Health Siphon, Rank 1', '_', 4, 0, 0, 6, 1, 'combat damage, heals self', 'This stackable debuff can be applied to your foe in combat, draining one life point from them each combat round, and awarding it to you.  It can be stacked up to three times.  +1 con.', 503, 1),
